      <title>美联储会议前黄金将连续第三个月上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/gold-set-to-gain-for-third-straight-month-ahead-of-fed-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于央行和避险需求强劲，黄金有望连续第三个月上涨，因为焦点转向本周的美联储利率决策会议，预计政策制定者将在会上采取鹰派基调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/gold-set-to-gain-for-third-straight-month-ahead-of-fed-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 01:36:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
